{"tid":49031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來屋企人係咁","createTime":"2016-12-21T12:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T14:43:22.000Z","uid":29496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78d670028978b7f070190e681df890f0a81b2a6d","tid":49031,"uid":29496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:05:49.000Z","msg":"岩岩一家4口係餐廳食飯 傾傾下佢地同我講1號要番大陸同呀公食飯 但我先醒起岩岩應承其他人1號幫手做大會攝影 咁我咪同屋企人講下次好啲講麻 我今日先應承左人做野 咁其實我都打算推工作咖啦 話晒親人點都重要啲 點知老豆就開口講 你去番工啦 咁勁下下咩應承街外人 反正食呀公既生日飯<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多你一個唔多</span></span>屋企你不嬲都唔理咖啦 聽完我嬲到唔知講咩同即刻離開番屋企 原來我係多餘"},{"pid":"0fe851de6f4d7eb0a1b7cfbce20ed2ae68279bd8","tid":49031,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:06:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9dd5742484780a20c51c348368cb82085bf9414f","tid":49031,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係咁"},{"pid":"05bc730062ebce81aeb5c0ee3971ac911ff370c9","tid":49031,"uid":25569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:09:13.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"fba3c3efffc22441def673f962b5b919fa309d35","tid":49031,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"成日睇呢d post就覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef79367674d10856558031fd92e194bed5db965","tid":49031,"uid":55593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:11:30.000Z","msg":"你老豆平時成日屌鳩你?"},{"pid":"e3cb08894b0ac56fb9530fa8351d347365862969","tid":49031,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日睇到呢d post就覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1fbc37197bffab842dea632ac435d264d154fb07","tid":49031,"uid":29496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re